headline: McCormick & Company's Q3 2025 Earnings: What to Expect
summary: McCormick & Company is scheduled to report its third-quarter results next month, and analysts expect a single-digit earnings decline.

headline: Shelf-Stable Food Stocks Q2 Teardown: McCormick (NYSE:MKC) Vs The Rest
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how shelf-stable food stocks fared in Q2, starting with McCormick (NYSE:MKC).
